cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SD 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on word reordering in statistical machine translation. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as these fields are closely related to NLP and SMT. Additionally, cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.SD (Sound) could be possible sub-categories as they also deal with language processing and modeling. However, these are less likely as the paper's focus is primarily on NLP and SMT.
